icationHeading\">Alerts In Effect</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Dismiss\" class=\"AlertsNotification__DismissButton\" type=\"button\">\nDismiss\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#close\"></use>\n</svg>\n</button>\n<span class=\"hr clearfix\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Body\" id=\"AlertsNotificationBody\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLinkContainer\">\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#add\"></use>\n</svg>\n<a class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLink\" href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/conditions.htm\" id=\"AlertsNotificationMoreLink\" tabindex=\"-1\">\nmore information on current conditions...\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"MainContent\" id=\"main\" role=\"main\">\n\n<div aria-labelledby=\"modal-contact-us-label\" class=\"modal fade\" id=\"modal-contact-us\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h4 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"modal-contact-us-label\">Contact Us</h4>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"adminTools\"></div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"ContentHeader text-content-size\">\n<h1 class=\"page-title\">Grand Canyon In Depth Video Series</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Layout\" id=\"cs_control_2\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"CS_Layout_Table\" id=\"cs_idLayout2\" summary=\"\" width=\"100%\"><tr class=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x1x1\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_2560947\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<font color=\"#556b2f\"><strong>Grand Canyon In Depth</strong></font> is a video podcast series that explores the natural and human history of Grand Canyon National Park. Join park rangers, scientists, and historians as they take us beyond the rim of the canyon to discover the diversity of life and the extraordinary beauty of Grand Canyon National Park.<br/>\n<br/>\nProduced by the <a href=\"https://www.nps.gov/index.htm\" id=\"https://www.nps.gov/index.htm|\">National Park Service</a> in association with <a href=\"http://www.bristleconemedia.com/\" id=\"http://www.bristleconemedia.com/|\">Bristlecone Media</a> and <a href=\"https://grandcanyon.org/\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1910307,https://grandcanyon.org/,11006|\" onmouseout=\"\" onmouseover=\"\">Grand Canyon Conservancy</a>, the official nonprofit partner of Grand Canyon National Park.\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_5920455\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_5920455\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<ul>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Episode 1: <a href=\"/grca/learn/photosmultimedia/grand-canyon-in-depth.htm#CP_JUMP_829707\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=2560571,grand-canyon-in-depth.htm#CP_JUMP_829707,14075|\">More Than A View</a></li>\n<li>Episode 2: <a href=\"/grca/learn/photosmultimedia/grand-canyon-in-depth.htm#CP_JUMP_829619\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=2560571,grand-canyon-in-depth.htm#CP_JUMP_829619,14075|\">Hidden Waters</a></li>\n<li>Episode 3: <a href=\"/grca/learn/photosmultimedia/grand-canyon-in-depth.htm#CP_JUMP_2592197\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=2560571,grand-canyon-in-depth.htm#CP_JUMP_2592197,14075|\">Phantom Ranch</a></li>\n<li>Episode 4: <a href=\"/grca/learn/photosmultimedia/grand-canyon-in-depth.htm#CP_JUMP_2616712\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=2560571,grand-canyon-in-depth.htm#CP_JUMP_2616712,14075|\">Night Sky</a></li>\n<li>Episode 5: <a href=\"/grca/learn/photosmultimedia/grand-canyon-in-depth.htm#CP_JUMP_829603\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=2560571,grand-canyon-in-depth.htm#CP_JUMP_829603,14075|\">Desert View Watchtower</a></li>\n<li>Episode 6: <a href=\"/grca/learn/photosmultimedia/grand-canyon-in-depth.htm#CP_JUMP_5190144\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=2560571,grand-canyon-in-depth.htm#CP_JUMP_5190144,14075|\">Pipeline on the Precipice</a></li>\n<li>Episode 7: <a href=\"/grca/learn/photosmultimedia/grand-canyon-in-depth.htm#CP_JUMP_5920431\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=2560571,grand-canyon-in-depth.htm#CP_JUMP_5920431,14075|\">North Rim</a></li>\n<li>Episode 8: <a href=\"/grca/learn/photosmultimedia/grand-canyon-in-depth.htm#CP_JUMP_5920432\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=2560571,grand-canyon-in-depth.htm#CP_JUMP_5920432,14075|\">Legacy</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_5920432\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<a id=\"e08\"></a><a id=\"CP_JUMP_5920432\"></a><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_5920432\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<hr align=\"left\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"1\" title=\"\"/>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_5283496\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_5283496\"> \n\n<div class=\"VideoHero\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/VideoObject\">\n<meta content=\"Legacy: Grand Canyon in Depth Episode 8\" itemprop=\"name\"/>\n<meta content=\"The Centennial of the National Park Service is an opportunity to reflect upon the conservation legacy of those who came before who protected these special lands, and to hear from present day Grand Canyon employees about what this means to them.\" itemprop=\"description\"/>\n<meta content=\"T6M53S\" itemprop=\"duration\"/>\n<meta content=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/grca/633E0498-1DD8-B71B-0BACF5922BCA06C8/grca-GCID08_splash.jpg\" itemprop=\"thumbnailUrl\"/>\n<meta content=\"https://www.nps.gov/media/video/view.htm?id=633E0498-1DD8-B71B-0BACF5922BCA06C8\" itemprop=\"embedURL\"/>\n<meta content=\"2020-10-14 00:00:00.0\" itemprop=\"uploadDate\"/>\n<div class=\"VideoHero-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin vjs-big-play-centered vjs-16-9\" controls=\"\" height=\"264\" id=\"av_633E04981DD8B71B0BACF5922BCA06C8\" poster=\"/common/uploads/imr/park/grca/63D667CB-1DD8-B71B-0BE827D806D5AD7C/63D667CB-1DD8-B71B-0BE827D806D5AD7C-large.jpg\" preload=\"metadata\" width=\"640\">\n<source label=\"720p\" res=\"720\" src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/grca/633E0498-1DD8-B71B-0BACF5922BCA06C8/grca-GCID08_1280x720.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"/>\n<source label=\"480p\" res=\"480\" src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/grca/633E0498-1DD8-B71B-0BACF5922BCA06C8/grca-GCID08_854x480.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"/>\n<source label=\"360p\" res=\"360\" src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/grca/633E0498-1DD8-B71B-0BACF5922BCA06C8/grca-GCID08_640x360.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"/>\n<source label=\"240p\" res=\"240\" src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/grca/633E0498-1DD8-B71B-0BACF5922BCA06C8/grca-GCID08_426x240.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"/>\n<track kind=\"captions\" label=\"English\" src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/closed-caption/imr/avElement/grca-LegacyEpisodeCaptions2.vtt\" srclang=\"en\"/>\n</video>\n<button aria-disabled=\"false\" aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"vjs-embed-control vjs-button\" data-bs-target=\"#av_633E04981DD8B71B0BACF5922BCA06C8EmbedModal\" data-bs-toggle=\"modal\" id=\"av_633E04981DD8B71B0BACF5922BCA06C8EmbedButton\" title=\"Embed Video\" type=\"button\">Embed</button>\n<div aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-labelledby=\"av_633E04981DD8B71B0BACF5922BCA06C8EmbedModalLabel\" class=\"modal fade VideoJSEmbedModal\" id=\"av_633E04981DD8B71B0BACF5922BCA06C8EmbedModal\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h1 class=\"modal-title\" id=\"av_633E04981DD8B71B0BACF5922BCA06C8EmbedModalLabel\">\nEmbed Video\n</h1>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n<textarea class=\"form-control\" id=\"av_633E04981DD8B71B0BACF5922BCA06C8EmbedText\" rows=\"6\"></textarea>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"VideoHero-text\">\n<a class=\"VideoHero-videoLink visuallyhidden\" href=\"/media/video/keyboard-shortcuts.htm\">Visit our keyboard shortcuts docs for details</a>\n<dl class=\"result-details wrapped\">\n<dt>Duration:</dt><dd>6 minutes, 53 seconds</dd>\n</dl>\n<p itemprop=\"description\">The Centennial of the National Park Service is an opportunity to reflect upon the conservation legacy of those who came before who protected these special lands, and to hear from present day Grand Canyon employees about what this means to them.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_5286268\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_5286268\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\nNot able to watch this program in this video player? It is also available on <strong><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XcJez9HxUY8\" id=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XcJez9HxUY8|\">YouTube</a></strong>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_5920431\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<a id=\"e07\"></a><a id=\"CP_JUMP_5920431\"></a><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_5920431\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<hr align=\"left\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"1\" title=\"\"/>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_5187788\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_5187788\">\n\n<div class=\"VideoHero\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/VideoObject\">\n<meta content=\"North Rim: Grand Canyon in Depth Episode 7\" itemprop=\"name\"/>\n<meta content=\"There is something about the North Rim of Grand Canyon that invokes a sense of solitude and serenity. This is a place that invites you to slow down, to ponder, to feel your own innate creativity, and to fall in love with landscape.\" itemprop=\"description\"/>\n<meta content=\"T8M21S\" itemprop=\"duration\"/>\n<meta content=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/grca/E16D4B1E-1DD8-B71B-0BDD246EA520AA01/grca-GCID07NR_splash.jpg\" itemprop=\"thumbnailUrl\"/>\n<meta content=\"https://www.nps.gov/media/video/view.htm?id=E16D4B1E-1DD8-B71B-0BDD246EA520AA01\" itemprop=\"embedURL\"/>\n<meta content=\"2020-10-14 00:00:00.0\" itemprop=\"uploadDate\"/>\n<div class=\"VideoHero-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin vjs-big-play-centered vjs-16-9\" controls=\"\" height=\"264\" id=\"av_E16D4B1E1DD8B71B0BDD246EA520AA01\" poster=\"/common/uploads/imr/park/grca/E1D91738-1DD8-B71B-0B9E3C0BC8F16AB5/E1D91738-1DD8-B71B-0B9E3C0BC8F16AB5-large.jpg\" preload=\"metadata\" width=\"640\">\n<source label=\"720p\" res=\"720\" src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/grca/E16D4B1E-1DD8-B71B-0BDD246EA520AA01/grca-GCID07NR_1280x720.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"/>\n<source label=\"480p\" res=\"480\" src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/grca/E16D4B1E-1DD8-B71B-0BDD246EA520AA01/grca-GCID07NR_854x480.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"/>\n<source label=\"360p\" res=\"360\" src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/grca/E16D4B1E-1DD8-B71B-0BDD246EA520AA01/grca-GCID07NR_640x360.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"/>\n<source label=\"240p\" res=\"240\" src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/grca/E16D4B1E-1DD8-B71B-0BDD246EA520AA01/grca-GCID07NR_426x240.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"/>\n<track kind=\"captions\" label=\"English\" src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/closed-caption/imr/avElement/grca-EPS07captions1.vtt\" srclang=\"en\"/>\n</video>\n<button aria-disabled=\"false\" aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"vjs-embed-control vjs-button\" data-bs-target=\"#av_E16D4B1E1DD8B71B0BDD246EA520AA01EmbedModal\" data-bs-toggle=\"modal\" id=\"av_E16D4B1E1DD8B71B0BDD246EA520AA01EmbedButton\" title=\"Embed Video\" type=\"button\">Embed</button>\n<div aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-labelledby=\"av_E16D4B1E1DD8B71B0BDD246EA520AA01EmbedModalLabel\" class=\"modal fade VideoJSEmbedModal\" id=\"av_E16D4B1E1DD8B71B0BDD246EA520AA01EmbedModal\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h1 class=\"modal-title\" id=\"av_E16D4B1E1DD8B71B0BDD246EA520AA01EmbedModalLabel\">\nEmbed Video\n</h1>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n<textarea class=\"form-control\" id=\"av_E16D4B1E1DD8B71B0BDD246EA520AA01EmbedText\" rows=\"6\"></textarea>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"VideoHero-text\">\n<a class=\"VideoHero-videoLink visuallyhidden\" href=\"/media/video/keyboard-shortcuts.htm\">Visit our keyboard shortcuts docs for details</a>\n<dl class=\"result-details wrapped\">\n<dt>Duration:</dt><dd>8 minutes, 21 seconds</dd>\n</dl>\n<p itemprop=\"description\">There is something about the North Rim of Grand Canyon that invokes a sense of solitude and serenity. This is a place that invites you to slow down, to ponder, to feel your own innate creativity, and to fall in love with landscape.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_5190146\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_5190146\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<strong>Not able to watch program in this video player?</strong><br/>\nWatch it on our YouTube channel here... <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iw5cDIskqBw\" id=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iw5cDIskqBw|\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iw5cDIskqBw</a>\n<p><a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/north-rim.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=837895,north-rim.htm,11006|\">Learn more about the North Rim</a>. North Rim <a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/cg-nr.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1954290,cg-nr.htm,11006|\">Camping</a> and <a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/lodging.htm#CP_JUMP_1968002\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1878476,lodging.htm#CP_JUMP_1968002,11006|\">Lodging.</a><br/>\n</p>\n<p> </p>\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iw5cDIskqBw\" id=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iw5cDIskqBw|\"></a>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_5190144\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<a id=\"e06\"></a><a id=\"CP_JUMP_5190144\"></a><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_5190144\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<hr align=\"left\" color=\"#000000\" size=\"1\" title=\"\"/>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_901153\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_901153\">\n\n<div class=\"VideoHero\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/VideoObject\">\n<meta content=\"Pipeline on the Precipice - Grand Canyon in Depth - Episode 6\" itemprop=\"name\"/>\n<meta content=\"The Trans-Canyon Pipeline was built in the late 1960's and supplies all of Grand Canyon National Park's potable water.  Over the past decade the pipeline has suffered numerous leaks, fissures, and breaks. Full replacement of the TCP is currently estimated at around $150 million. \n&quot;Guaranteed water to the South Rim is in peril as long as we have the existing pipeline and infrastructure in place. If we don’t have that, then everybody goes home.&quot; Grand Canyon N.P. Sup't Dave Uberuaga,\" itemprop=\"description\"/>\n<meta content=\"T9M3S\" itemprop=\"duration\"/>\n<meta content=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/grca/25F8AD9C-1DD8-B71B-0BA48D3BE7A1EE92/grca-GCID6-720Master2_splash.jpg\" itemprop=\"thumbnailUrl\"/>\n<meta content=\"https://www.nps.gov/media/video/view.htm?id=25F8AD9C-1DD8-B71B-0BA48D3BE7A1EE92\" itemprop=\"embedURL\"/>\n<meta content=\"2020-10-14 00:00:00.0\" itemprop=\"uploadDate\"/>\n<div class=\"VideoHero-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin vjs-big-play-centered vjs-16-9\" controls=\"\" height=\"264\" id=\"av_25F8AD9C1DD8B71B0BA48D3BE7A1EE92\" poster=\"/common/uploads/imr/park/grca/C7788F7A-1DD8-B71B-0B2D2D58433BAC71/C7788F7A-1DD8-B71B-0B2D2D58433BAC71-large.jpg\" preload=\"metadata\" width=\"640\">\n<source label=\"720p\" res=\"720\" src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/grca/25F8AD9C-1DD8-B71B-0BA48D3BE7A1EE92/grca-GCID6-720Master2_1280x720.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"/>\n<source label=\"480p\" res=\"480\" src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/grca/25F8AD9C-1DD8-B71B-0BA48D3BE7A1EE92/grca-GCID6-720Master2_854x480.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"/>\n<source label=\"360p\" res=\"360\" src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/grca/25F8AD9C-1DD8-B71B-0BA48D3BE7A1EE92/grca-GCID6-720Master2_640x360.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"/>\n<source label=\"240p\" res=\"240\" src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/grca/25F8AD9C-1DD8-B71B-0BA48D3BE7A1EE92/grca-GCID6-720Master2_426x240.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"/>\n<track kind=\"captions\" label=\"English\" src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/closed-caption/imr/avElement/grca-GCID6-720Master2.vtt\" srclang=\"en\"/>\n</video>\n<button aria-disabled=\"false\" aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"vjs-embed-control vjs-button\" data-bs-target=\"#av_25F8AD9C1DD8B71B0BA48D3BE7A1EE92EmbedModal\" data-bs-toggle=\"modal\" id=\"av_25F8AD9C1DD8B71B0BA48D3BE7A1EE92EmbedButton\" title=\"Embed Video\" type=\"button\">Embed</button>\n<div aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-labelledby=\"av_25F8AD9C1DD8B71B0BA